OBID® and OBID i-scan® are registered trademarks of FEIG ELECTRONIC GmbH.


Each Reader command is built by a sequence of command parameters. The values of the parameters can be set with overloaded methods which passes a string from the package de.feig.ReaderCommand representing the name of the command parameter. All names of command parameters of all OBID® readers are unified and divided in hierarchical order in groups and subgroups separated by a dot.

For more general information, please refer to the system manual of the Reader.
